{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_09_01",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 1話 一緒に頑張ろうって言ったでしょ？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君！\n怜ちゃんの怪我はどうだった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}!\nHow’s Rei’s injury?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "幸いなことに、大したことはありませんでした\n一通り検査は受けて、今は寮で休んでますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fortunately‚ it wasn’t serious.\nShe got a full checkup and is resting at the dorm now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.0359303672,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ただ……怪我はともかく過労気味だったので\nしばらくは安静にということでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However… aside from her injury‚ she was overworked‚ so…\nThe doctor said she needs to rest for a while.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.9799322605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "良かった\n……でも過労って、ここ最近練習し過ぎだったせいよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s good to hear…\n…But being overworked means she must've been practicing too much lately.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.1666669528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "心配だわ……寮に帰ったら\n遙子特製栄養ドリンクでも差し入れようかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm worried… When I get back to the dorm‚\nI wonder if I should bring her some of Haruko's special nutrient drink?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.4666669528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "料理上手な遙子さんなら心配ないと思いますけど……\n一応、材料を聞いてもいいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sure it’ll be fine if it’s from talented cook Haruko-san…\nCould I ask what the ingredients are?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.4367578666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん。まずはマムシに青汁、にんにくでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. First of all‚ pit vipers‚ green juice‚ garlic‚ right!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.2700911999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……それはやめておきましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Let’s not do that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.9856921037,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、もちろん冗談よ\n安心して少し気が緩んじゃったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ of course I’m kidding.\nI guess I let my guard down a bit because I was relieved.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.5333336194,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "私も病院まで付き添えれば良かったんだけど\n次のお仕事を休む訳にはいかなかったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wish I could have accompanied her to the hospital too‚\nBut I couldn’t miss my next job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.9490564221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんの無事が分かって、やっと安心出来たわ\nありがとうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was finally able to relax when I found out Rei-chan was safe.\nThank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.3350928761,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、怪我が良くなるまでは\nちゃーんと見張っておかないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But until she recovers from her injury‚\nWe have to keep a close eye on her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.2195208603,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんてば\n目を離すとすぐ自主練始めちゃうんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei-chan‚\nShe starts practicing on her own as soon as I take my eyes off her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.8116416836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね、俺も気を付けておきます\n体調の回復が第一ですからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know. I’ll be careful too.\nRecovering her health is the top priority.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.7028200309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "前もってフォロー出来ていれば一番良かったんですが\n遙子さんまで不安にさせてしまって、すみませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wish I had been able to support her in advance‚\nI’m sorry for making you worry‚ Haruko-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.6028200309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、謝らないで。私だってそばについてたのに\n怜ちゃんに怪我をさせてしまったし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ don’t apologize. I was by her side‚\nBut I let Rei-chan get hurt…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.7333407402,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "だからその分、怜ちゃんが回復するまでの間は\nお互い頑張っていきましょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So until Rei-chan recovers‚\nlet's both work hard.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.2333407402,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "まずは、怜ちゃんが入る予定だったお仕事を\nみんなで穴埋めしていかないとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First of all‚ we have to fill in for Rei-chan\non all her jobs.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.4135938576,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね、俺の方でスケジュールを組んでみます\n遙子さんにも相談させてもらいますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay. I’ll put together a schedule.\nI’ll consult with you too‚ Haruko-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.8636652469,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8036.334753100007,
          "startTime": 124.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そういえば、今回のユニット曲のジャケット撮影の\n日が決まりましたよ。コンセプトも届いています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ right. The date has been set for the jacket shoot\nfor the new unit song. The concept has also been sent over.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.0969985802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "日にちは……この頃なら、怜ちゃんも復帰してそうね\nコンセプトも見せてもらえるかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The date is… around this time‚ so it seems like Rei-chan will be back by then.\nCan you show me the concept?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.0000130017,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6433.320331599987,
          "startTime": 139.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ミニチュアの街を使った撮影だそうですよ\nこれが大まかなイメージで――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They said the shoot will be in a miniature city.\nHere’s a general image――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.7601735274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "…………大怪獣ってことかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…………Does that mean I'm a giant monster?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.0934905847,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "え？　大怪獣……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Giant monster…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.3268920581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "ミニチュアの街で撮影って、怪獣映画みたいじゃない？\nこういうのが私のイメージってことなのかしら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Doesn’t shooting in a miniature city seem like a monster movie?\nIs this supposed to be my image…？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.7000160535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "大きくて、むちむちしてて\n食欲旺盛で、なんでも食べちゃうような……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Big‚ plump‚\nwith a huge appetite‚ eating everything…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.1000160535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "むちむち怪獣ハルドン、っていうことなのかしら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I’m like… a plump monster…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.8093413353,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "誰もそんなこと言ってないですよ！？\n別に怪獣とも限りませんし、ほら、ヒーローの線も！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nobody said anything like that!?\nIt’s not necessarily a monster‚ look‚ there’s a hero side too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.0992507617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "むちむちは？　むちむちは否定してくれないのね！？\nヒーローの線でも、むちむちなのは変わらないのね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Plump? You’re not denying the plump part!?\nEven if I'm on the hero side‚ I'm still plump‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.9000160535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "あ……そ、そういう訳では……！\n遙子さんは、むちむちなんてしてませんよ、えぇ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… Th-That’s not…!\nHaruko-san‚ you’re not plump at all‚ yeah!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.282629935,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか無理矢理言わせたみたいになってる……\n……なんてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It sounds like I'm forcing you to say it…\n…Just kidding.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.2333504041,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-hrk020.m4a",
      "text": "この撮影なら、激しい動きはなさそうだし\n回復した怜ちゃんに無理をさせずに済みそうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This shoot doesn't seem to involve any strenuous movements‚\nso it looks like we can avoid putting any strain on Rei-chan when she recovers.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.1000130018,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-hrk021.m4a",
      "text": "……まだちょっと、コンセプトには納得してないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But I’m still not quite convinced about the concept.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.3240270298,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "納得してないんですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re not convinced…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 212.7087663651,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
