      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-hrk025.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫よ。この間まで怜ちゃんと練習してたおかげで\n今まで以上に体力もついてるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s okay. Thanks to all the practice I’ve been doing with Rei-chan lately‚\nI’m in better shape than ever.",
